'''Sinte''' (Sinti) si [[Romane manusha]] so avilen (15to [[shelbersh]]este) kay akanutne [[them]]a [[Jermaniya]] tay [[Estrexa]]. Palal kodya rigyarden pen pe duy droma: le ''Eftavagarya'' tay le ''Estraxarya''. Le Eftavagarya gelen ki akanutni [[Franchiya]] kay xamomen le thanutne romensa, navyarde [[Manusha]]. Le Estraxarya gelen kay [[Italiya]] tay [[Estutni Europa]] buteder kay thema [[Kroatiya]], [[Ungariya]], [[Transilvaniya]], [[Chexiya]] tay [[Slovakiya]].

Mashkar lenge si bare [[bashavno|bashavne]] vay [[gilavno|gilavne]], sar sas o [[Django Reinhardt]], vi ando khelsastimasko (sportesko) umal, sar o [[Johann  Trollmann|Johann Rukeli Trollmann]]

